description: The Deka Euro Corporates 0-3 Liquid UCITS ETF is a UCITS IV-compliant mutual fund that replicates the performance of the Solactive Euro Corporates 0-3 Year Liquid EUR (price index). The index tracks the market for euro-denominated, short-term corporate bonds and includes 90 liquid bonds with a remaining term of between three months and three years.
name: Deka Euro Corporates 0-3 Liquid UCITS ETF
